text: Adyam Tesfalem (born 17 January 1997) is an Eritrean road racing cyclist. She competed at the 2021 UCI Road World Championships, in the women's time trial event and women's road race event. After winning the silver medal in 2019, she became 2021 Eritrean National Time Trial Champion. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Cyclists Category:Living people
